<li>I'm incredibly thankful for the love and support you've always shown me.</li>
<li>So grateful for the memories we've made together this year.  Here's to many more!</li>
<li>My heart overflows with thankfulness for my amazing family.  Happy Thanksgiving!</li>
<li>This year, I'm especially grateful for your endless patience and understanding.</li>
<li>Thank you for being my rock, my confidante, and my biggest cheerleader.</li>
<li>Happy Thanksgiving to the best family a person could ask for!</li>
<li>Your love and kindness are the greatest gifts I could ever receive.</li>
<li>I cherish our time together more than words can say. Happy Thanksgiving, family!</li>
<li>Feeling truly blessed to have such a loving and supportive family.</li>
